Will change netem config on the fly
s0 s0-eth2
Router Router-eth0
boxes s0 Router
sleep 0.1 && tc qdisc add dev s0-eth1 root handle 1:0 netem loss 0% delay 30ms 0ms && tc qdisc show >> ping.log
sleep 0.1 && tc qdisc del dev s0-eth2 root  && tc qdisc add dev s0-eth2 root netem loss 0% delay 30ms 0ms && tc qdisc show >> ping.log
